NAME
    Template::Plugin::Markdown

SYNOPSIS
            [% USE Markdown %]
            [% markdowntext = "# Hello, world!" %]
            [% markdowntext | md2html %]
            # => <h1>Hello, world!</h1>

DESCRIPTION
    Template::Plugin::Markdown is a small filter to convert markdown to
    html.

